# GitHub Copilot Instructions — Finance Video Generator

## Project Overview

Automated AI-powered finance video creation system.
**Stack:** TypeScript · Node.js v20+ · Remotion · Vercel AI SDK + GPT-4o · ElevenLabs · Runway · Epidemic Sound · Sharp · Express.js · Zod

## Pipeline

```
Script (generateObject + Zod) → Audio (ElevenLabs) + B-roll (Runway / Sharp fallback) → Compose (Remotion)
```

## Critical Rules

### ✅ Always use `generateObject()` with Zod schemas
```typescript
import { generateObject } from 'ai';
import { openai } from '@ai-sdk/openai';
import { z } from 'zod';

const { object } = await generateObject({
  model: openai('gpt-4o'),
  schema: z.object({
    scenes: z.array(z.object({
      id: z.number(),
      description: z.string(),
      duration: z.number(),
      voiceScript: z.string(),
    })),
    musicGenre: z.string(),
  }),
  prompt: "Generate a finance video script...",
});
```

❌ Never use `generateText()` or parse unstructured text.

### ✅ Always use environment variables
```typescript
const apiKey = process.env.OPENAI_API_KEY;
if (!apiKey) throw new Error('OPENAI_API_KEY not set');
```

### ✅ Exponential backoff for ElevenLabs 429s
```typescript
for (let i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
  try {
    return await elevenLabsClient.textToSpeech.convert({ text, voice_id });
  } catch (e: any) {
    if (e.status === 429 && i < 4) await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2 ** i * 1000));
    else throw e;
  }
}
```

### ✅ Verify assets before Remotion render
```typescript
import { existsSync } from 'fs';
const source = existsSync(videoPath) ? videoPath : '#FF6B6B'; // color fallback
```

### ✅ Respect Epidemic Sound rate-limit headers
```typescript
const remaining = parseInt(res.headers.get('X-RateLimit-Remaining') || '0');
const reset = parseInt(res.headers.get('X-RateLimit-Reset') || '0');
if (remaining < 10) await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, reset - Date.now()));
```

